'''Jamie Kiefer''' was in the hospital after an appendectomy.

==History==
===Post-Op Symptoms===
Jamie had an appendectomy that went well and her incision was healing well three days later. However, she had a sore throat that was concerning Dr. Bailey. Dr. Bailey assured Jamie's mother that it was probably just an infection, but she planned to keep Jamie there another day to run some tests because she had swelling, which was abnormal. Bailey called [[Arizona Robbins]], who was still at home recovering, for a consult. Arizona diagnosed Lemierre's disease.

==Notes and Trivia==
*She was 13 at the time of her hospitalization.
